    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though it could benefit from a tune-up as the idle is occasionally inconsistent. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and clear coat peeling on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant staining and wear on the driver's seat. While it is currently roadworthy, please expect to invest in some minor repairs and cosmetic detailing to bring it back to its best.",
