    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This car is looking for a fresh start and a dedicated new owner to bring it back to life. While it's currently in poor condition and requires significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it's the perfect blank canvas for your next automotive restoration. Grab this opportunity to build your dream ride from the ground up at a great price!",
