    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the professional driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, this model offers a sophisticated balance of performance and reliability. It remains a definitive choice for those who demand quality and poise in a pre-owned executive vehicle.",
      "price": 34900.0,
